author: DAVID PITT and RYAN J. FOLEY Associated Press
title: Pressure mounting for Iowa stay-at-home order from governor
description: DES MOINES, Iowa (AP) — Pressure from medical experts and politicians mounted Thursday on Iowa Gov. Kim Reynolds to issue a statewide stay-at-home order, despite her repeated insistence that such a move isn't necessary.
